300
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,600
How can we keep up with the world champion?

301
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:38,000
So I arrange a relay run.

302
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,700
So there's not much running to do

303
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,720
