304
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:43,080
How long will we be running?

305
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:45,220
Probably over ten kilometers.

306
00:17:45,220 --> 00:17:46,560
Let's just call it ten kilometers.

307
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:48,880
So the six of us have to run

308
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:53,000
