318
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,000
So each of us

319
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,480
has to run more, right?

320
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,200
Mr. Chen, Peilan.

321
00:18:19,104 --> 00:18:20,120
I know this is

322
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:22,120
