323
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:24,840
Especially the hospital work
is so heavy these days.

324
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,240
- So--
- So,

325
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:28,080
we have to do this.

326
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:31,120
Well, it's not the first time

327
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:32,120
Tianlin has done something like this.

328
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:36,200
Aunt, come on and sit.

329
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,560
- Sit.
