333
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:45,360
Why don't you, Mr. Chen, run some for her?

334
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,640
I can take care of it for you.

335
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,440
I don't run for nothing.

336
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,320
I'll run three kilometers.

337
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,720
Tian, you're young.

338
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:55,680
Don't you want to run an extra kilometer

339
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,520
for Wen Jing and Tian Tian?

340
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,600
No need.

341
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:02,600
When I was at school,
I was the girls' 3km race champion.

342
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:04,740
Two kilometers shouldn't be a problem.

343
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:07,440
You are that great?
Why didn't you say it earlier?

344
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,240
Wen Jing, then you can run more for me.

345
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:10,480
Can you be a man?

346
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:11,800
- You're a man.
- Can you be a man?

347
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,720
You're the only young man.

348
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,880
You should run an extra two kilometers.

349
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,880
Chen Yifan, you push me.

350
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,280
Come on, I'll push you.

351
00:19:38,464 --> 00:19:39,488
Is it okay?

352
00:19:39,488 --> 00:19:40,576
Okay.

353
00:19:40,576 --> 00:19:41,720
Well done.

354
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:45,040
Let's try it for Mr. Yan and Champion.

355
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:47,440
Come on, okay.

356
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:50,000
Let's do it again.

357
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,200
Come here, this way.

358
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,440
Wheelchair!

359
00:19:59,616 --> 00:20:00,640
Come on.

360
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,640
Are you okay, Mr. Chen?

361
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,680
Are you okay?

362
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,600
Mr. Yan and Champion
are really having a hard time.

363
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:06,400
If you are okay, let's try again.

364
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,480
Let's try it again.

365
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,840
Okay, come on.

366
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:12,384
Let's go.

367
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,880
Director Zhang, thank you
