371
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,840
We must fully support

372
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,880
such a meaningful event.

373
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,360
Thank you.

374
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:34,880
<i>[First Tianlin International Marathon,
Starting Point]</i>

