00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:31,240
We almost reach Mr. Chen.

439
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,920
Over here, Tian.

440
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,464
Tian.

441
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:40,960
Good work.

442
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,140
You're the best.

443
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,440
Keep going.

