00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,920
Mr. Yan, are you okay?

483
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:02,976
Yes.

484
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,740
Tian Tian.

485
00:27:07,740 --> 00:27:08,840
